1
00:00:21,000 --> 00:00:21,960
This is the Lu Family estate.

2
00:00:22,480 --> 00:00:24,480
Can any random nobody just waltz in here?

3
00:00:25,039 --> 00:00:26,920
Someone, throw him out right now!

4
00:00:27,679 --> 00:00:29,120
You've got no say in Lu Family matters.

5
00:00:32,840 --> 00:00:33,560
Mr. Ren.

6
00:00:36,880 --> 00:00:37,799
May I give it a try?

7
00:00:42,600 --> 00:00:43,000
Please.

8
00:01:21,920 --> 00:01:22,680
Done.

9
00:01:31,120 --> 00:01:31,719
Impressive technique!

10
00:01:33,840 --> 00:01:36,000
I couldn't even see how he made the cut.

11
00:01:36,319 --> 00:01:36,920
That's incredible.

12
00:01:36,920 --> 00:01:38,239
He's really skilled.

13
00:01:39,120 --> 00:01:39,920
How is that possible?

14
00:01:40,719 --> 00:01:41,480
Mr. Ren,

15
00:01:42,359 --> 00:01:43,920
is your surgical skill a family tradition?

16
00:01:45,560 --> 00:01:47,599
From the Chinese clinic, Premier Medical Hall?

17
00:01:48,560 --> 00:01:49,359
Don't be ridiculous.

18
00:01:50,000 --> 00:01:51,239
Chinese clinics never perform surgery.

19
00:01:51,920 --> 00:01:54,959
China had cranial surgery back in the Shang and Zhou dynasties.

20
00:01:55,560 --> 00:01:56,319
In the second century AD,

21
00:01:57,000 --> 00:01:57,719
Hua Tuo of the Han Dynasty

22
00:01:57,719 --> 00:02:01,359
performed the world's first abdominal surgery under general anesthesia.

23
00:02:01,760 --> 00:02:04,879
Europe didn't adopt anesthetic surgery until the 19th century.

24
00:02:05,280 --> 00:02:08,759
Chinese medicine mastered surgery a thousand years before Europe.

25
00:02:09,159 --> 00:02:09,879
Well said.

26
00:02:10,520 --> 00:02:11,240
However,

27
00:02:12,879 --> 00:02:14,400
the Ancient Chinese Medical Arts I've studied

28
00:02:15,120 --> 00:02:15,879
don't require surgery

29
00:02:16,520 --> 00:02:18,159
to cure Elder Lu's eyes.

30
00:02:20,000 --> 00:02:21,599
A physician mustn't speak recklessly.

31
00:02:22,120 --> 00:02:22,960
If anything goes wrong,

32
00:02:23,360 --> 00:02:24,240
do you know the consequences?

33
00:02:25,800 --> 00:02:26,199
Of course.

34
00:02:38,919 --> 00:02:40,919
Elder Lu suffers from liver and kidney deficiency,

35
00:02:41,000 --> 00:02:41,879
lacking vital essence,

36
00:02:42,280 --> 00:02:43,479
which has deprived the eyes of nourishment,

37
00:02:43,800 --> 00:02:44,639
forming internal cataracts.

38
00:02:45,479 --> 00:02:46,680
To treat cataracts with acupuncture,

39
00:02:47,479 --> 00:02:51,120
needles are inserted into the Jingming, Cuanzhu, and Taiyang points.

40
00:02:52,639 --> 00:02:55,199
The liver governs the eyes; the kidney governs essence.

41
00:02:55,919 --> 00:02:56,840
Acupuncture regulates and restores,

42
00:02:57,439 --> 00:02:58,639
using the nature of the needle

43
00:02:59,000 --> 00:03:00,400
to stimulate liver and kidney energies,

44
00:03:00,919 --> 00:03:02,240
thereby nourishing the liver and kidney,

45
00:03:02,319 --> 00:03:03,439
clearing the ocular channels,

46
00:03:03,879 --> 00:03:05,400
and restoring sight.

47
00:03:06,479 --> 00:03:07,080
The final step:

48
00:03:07,719 --> 00:03:09,159
from the Ancient Chinese Medical Arts,

49
00:03:09,360 --> 00:03:10,360
the Golden Spatula Cataract Surgery.

50
00:03:20,439 --> 00:03:20,960
How is it?

51
00:03:21,639 --> 00:03:21,960
Dad,

52
00:03:22,479 --> 00:03:23,240
can you see now?

53
00:03:25,879 --> 00:03:27,199
I can see.

54
00:03:27,199 --> 00:03:28,080
I can see now!

55
00:03:28,080 --> 00:03:28,919
I can see!

56
00:03:29,280 --> 00:03:30,319
I can see!

57
00:03:32,360 --> 00:03:32,919
Amazing.

58
00:03:32,919 --> 00:03:33,919
Truly astonishing.

59
00:03:34,680 --> 00:03:35,479
Incredible.

60
00:03:41,479 --> 00:03:42,400
Young man,

61
00:03:43,680 --> 00:03:45,360
I owe it all to you.

62
00:03:46,879 --> 00:03:49,080
Thank you, thank you.

63
00:03:50,199 --> 00:03:52,879
Jianqi, thank him for me.

64
00:03:54,000 --> 00:03:55,319
Mr. Ren, please.

65
00:04:15,199 --> 00:04:15,639
Please,

66
00:04:19,800 --> 00:04:21,680
first deliver the patent license,

67
00:04:22,000 --> 00:04:23,519
then treat my father.

68
00:04:24,120 --> 00:04:25,800
I don't believe this is a coincidence.

69
00:04:27,519 --> 00:04:29,000
Delivering the patent license,

70
00:04:29,560 --> 00:04:30,680
I do have an agenda.

71
00:04:31,199 --> 00:04:32,759
But in treating your father,

72
00:04:33,360 --> 00:04:34,600
I have no ulterior motive.

73
00:04:36,079 --> 00:04:37,720
It's simply a healer's conscience.

74
00:04:38,600 --> 00:04:39,079
Good.

75
00:04:40,439 --> 00:04:42,120
I like sincere, clever people.

76
00:04:43,920 --> 00:04:44,959
What do you want?

77
00:04:46,279 --> 00:04:46,959
What I want

78
00:04:47,959 --> 00:04:49,839
is trivial for you.

79
00:04:50,720 --> 00:04:52,120
I want to join Beisheng'an Hospital.

80
00:04:53,519 --> 00:04:54,319
That's all?

81
00:05:01,560 --> 00:05:03,519
Do you know what this license

82
00:05:04,120 --> 00:05:04,879
you gave me represents?

83
00:05:07,000 --> 00:05:07,639
Last year,

84
00:05:09,000 --> 00:05:12,319
your proprietary Chinese respiratory medicine,

85
00:05:12,560 --> 00:05:13,199
in South City,

86
00:05:13,519 --> 00:05:14,600
within one year of launch,

87
00:05:14,600 --> 00:05:16,759
the distributor closed three funding rounds.

88
00:05:18,000 --> 00:05:19,600
The entire South City Chamber of Commerce

89
00:05:19,720 --> 00:05:21,839
was commended because of this drug.

90
00:05:22,079 --> 00:05:23,560
Bringing them unmatched glory.

91
00:05:25,560 --> 00:05:27,279
Now you're giving it to me,

92
00:05:28,199 --> 00:05:30,759
asking only to join Beisheng'an Hospital.

93
00:05:32,319 --> 00:05:34,360
As chairman of North City's Medical Association,

94
00:05:34,959 --> 00:05:36,800
you founded Lubei Pharmaceutical last year

95
00:05:37,120 --> 00:05:39,000
out of dissatisfaction with a few oligarchs

96
00:05:39,000 --> 00:05:41,160
using foreign capital to monopolize the market.

97
00:05:41,800 --> 00:05:43,399
So this license of mine

98
00:05:43,759 --> 00:05:44,920
shares the same purpose as yours,

99
00:05:45,920 --> 00:05:48,879
to change the gloom over North City's medical industry.

100
00:05:50,240 --> 00:05:50,720
Good.

101
00:05:53,959 --> 00:05:54,759
Well said.

102
00:05:57,560 --> 00:06:00,800
Actually, your father Ren Fanghai and I go way back.

103
00:06:02,160 --> 00:06:05,199
In private, don't call me chairman anymore.

104
00:06:05,759 --> 00:06:06,839
Just call me Uncle Lu.

105
00:06:07,600 --> 00:06:09,240
Alright, Uncle Lu.

106
00:06:11,879 --> 00:06:13,560
At Beisheng'an Hospital,

107
00:06:13,800 --> 00:06:16,240
what position do you think would suit you?

108
00:06:37,480 --> 00:06:39,040
Hello, Director Ren.

109
00:06:41,920 --> 00:06:43,000
Thank you all for your kindness.

110
00:06:43,399 --> 00:06:45,079
Everyone, get back to work.

111
00:06:46,480 --> 00:06:48,040
Alright, let's go.

112
00:06:50,879 --> 00:06:52,079
Not bad, kid.

113
00:06:52,240 --> 00:06:54,160
Just got out and you're already my boss.

114
00:06:55,199 --> 00:06:57,399
It was easier than I thought.

115
00:06:59,600 --> 00:07:00,399
By the way, Senior Brother.

116
00:07:01,160 --> 00:07:03,519
There's something I need your help with.

117
00:07:04,759 --> 00:07:07,319
Starting today, keep a close eye on Ren Feifan.

118
00:07:08,439 --> 00:07:11,079
I want to see how long he can keep this up.

119
00:07:13,160 --> 00:07:15,480
Don't go easy on Ren Feifan.

120
00:07:16,399 --> 00:07:17,759
Do I make myself clear?

121
00:07:20,160 --> 00:07:21,319
What exactly are you trying to find?

122
00:07:22,079 --> 00:07:24,759
The Wang Family stole a prescription from us back then.

123
00:07:25,000 --> 00:07:26,439
But I don't know exactly which one.

124
00:07:26,720 --> 00:07:27,319
A prescription.

125
00:07:29,040 --> 00:07:30,120
So you spent the whole day checking

126
00:07:30,120 --> 00:07:32,240
the herb usage at the new drug research center

127
00:07:32,839 --> 00:07:35,040
to figure out what herbs were in that prescription?

128
00:07:35,360 --> 00:07:35,879
That's right.

129
00:07:37,560 --> 00:07:39,360
Isn't that like finding a needle in a haystack?

130
00:07:40,839 --> 00:07:41,639
By the way, Senior Brother.

131
00:07:41,879 --> 00:07:43,319
You were familiar with our family's situation back then.

132
00:07:43,720 --> 00:07:45,920
Can you guess which prescription it was?

133
00:07:48,480 --> 00:07:49,439
I don't know either.

134
00:07:52,240 --> 00:07:52,800
Alright.

135
00:07:53,600 --> 00:07:54,600
You should head back first.

136
00:07:54,680 --> 00:07:55,439
I'll keep looking for a while.

137
00:07:55,639 --> 00:07:57,680
Okay, but don't stay too late.

138
00:07:58,199 --> 00:07:59,439
This can't be rushed.

139
00:07:59,800 --> 00:08:00,600
Don't wear yourself out.

140
00:08:12,920 --> 00:08:14,319
File corrupted.

141
00:08:16,000 --> 00:08:17,399
File corrupted.

142
00:08:23,240 --> 00:08:24,120
Hello, is this the archives?

143
00:08:24,120 --> 00:08:24,720
Hello.

144
00:08:24,720 --> 00:08:27,439
Do you have the paper copy of ZXR 1158?

145
00:08:27,920 --> 00:08:28,560
Oh, yes, we do.

146
00:08:28,839 --> 00:08:30,839
Great, I'll come pick it up now.

147
00:08:30,839 --> 00:08:31,279
Okay.

148
00:08:57,519 --> 00:08:57,919
Hello?

149
00:08:58,399 --> 00:08:59,360
The nurse in the archive room passed out.

150
00:08:59,639 --> 00:09:00,159
But it's nothing serious.

151
00:09:00,240 --> 00:09:01,120
Come up and take care of it.

152
00:09:01,120 --> 00:09:01,600
Got it.

153
00:09:17,240 --> 00:09:18,039
Stop right there!

154
00:09:20,600 --> 00:09:21,200
Stop!

155
00:10:01,480 --> 00:10:02,279
Shen Yue.

156
00:10:02,840 --> 00:10:04,799
Long time no see, Feifan.

157
00:10:08,720 --> 00:10:10,360
Hand over what you just stole.

158
00:10:11,879 --> 00:10:13,399
Why are you being so rough?

159
00:10:16,080 --> 00:10:17,360
You're hurting me.

160
00:10:21,720 --> 00:10:22,960
You're accusing me of stealing?

161
00:10:23,440 --> 00:10:24,440
What did I steal?

162
00:10:25,519 --> 00:10:26,080
Director.

163
00:10:27,080 --> 00:10:28,519
If you don't believe me,

164
00:10:29,159 --> 00:10:30,440
you're welcome to search me.

165
00:10:32,519 --> 00:10:33,080
Hand it over.

166
00:10:33,679 --> 00:10:34,720
Feifan.

167
00:10:35,600 --> 00:10:39,039
Those are just the hospital's public records.

168
00:10:39,879 --> 00:10:41,639
They're of no use to you.

169
00:10:43,879 --> 00:10:45,759
Shen Yue, don't make trouble for me.

170
00:10:46,120 --> 00:10:46,840
Otherwise...

171
00:10:47,159 --> 00:10:47,840
Otherwise what?

172
00:10:57,799 --> 00:10:58,519
You're welcome.

173
00:11:09,320 --> 00:11:10,879
Okay, got it.

174
00:11:11,559 --> 00:11:12,440
It's all up to you then.

175
00:11:13,200 --> 00:11:13,679
Mm.

176
00:12:11,320 --> 00:12:14,559
The newly appointed Director Ren Feifan

177
00:12:17,080 --> 00:12:18,679
I'll go feel him out

178
00:12:40,159 --> 00:12:41,320
Ma-ma'am, are you all right?

179
00:12:42,320 --> 00:12:43,720
I think I sprained my ankle.

180
00:12:44,559 --> 00:12:45,039
Let me take a look.

181
00:12:52,120 --> 00:12:52,960
That hurts!

182
00:12:58,519 --> 00:12:59,320
It hurts so much!

183
00:13:02,679 --> 00:13:03,879
Your ankle is fine.

184
00:13:03,879 --> 00:13:05,960
Just try to wear high heels less.

185
00:13:06,759 --> 00:13:08,799
But it really hurts.

186
00:13:09,519 --> 00:13:10,919
Could you take me home?

187
00:13:14,960 --> 00:13:15,759
I've got a fierce wife at home.

188
00:13:16,240 --> 00:13:16,879
It's not very appropriate.

189
00:13:17,759 --> 00:13:19,840
Why are you so boring?

190
00:13:21,440 --> 00:13:22,039
I've got things to do.

191
00:13:22,480 --> 00:13:23,519
You'd better ask someone else.

192
00:13:27,480 --> 00:13:28,200
How dull.

193
00:13:28,480 --> 00:13:30,679
So guarded... Something's definitely off.

194
00:13:31,919 --> 00:13:35,000
These are the Li family's herb supply records.

195
00:13:36,960 --> 00:13:40,519
But it doesn't say who the herbs were supplied to.

196
00:13:40,799 --> 00:13:44,200
Sichuan Aconite Root and Pinellia Rhizome are toxic herbs containing aconitine.

197
00:13:44,639 --> 00:13:46,440
Their harvest has been strictly banned.

198
00:13:47,480 --> 00:13:48,679
These herbs...

199
00:13:48,679 --> 00:13:50,879
only started appearing in records four years ago.

200
00:13:52,080 --> 00:13:54,519
They must be linked to the prescription the Wang Family stole.

201
00:14:03,000 --> 00:14:03,679
Hey, Da Zhuang.

202
00:14:04,639 --> 00:14:05,919
I need you to look into something for me.

